WEBVTT

00:01:16.480 --> 00:01:17.320
Dying.

00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:19.840
Will it hurt a lot?

00:01:24.080 --> 00:01:24.960
Isn't living

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:26.840
painful enough?

00:01:29.760 --> 00:01:30.920
But back then,

00:01:31.880 --> 00:01:33.479
why did we hesitate?

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:43.080
I didn't hesitate.

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:46.360
I'm already ruined.

00:01:47.600 --> 00:01:50.560
This world no longer has any meaning to me.

00:01:53.840 --> 00:01:54.640
Meaning

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:56.600
isn't in our rotting flesh.

00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:57.840
It lies in

00:01:57.880 --> 00:01:59.479
a girl who wanted to live more than us,

00:01:59.479 --> 00:02:01.600
but died a much more tragic death.

00:02:01.600 --> 00:02:02.120
Guan...

00:02:04.640 --> 00:02:05.280
Guannan.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:07.160
Our pain

00:02:07.400 --> 00:02:09.400
is like a blunt knife cutting flesh.

00:02:09.600 --> 00:02:10.639
Her pain

00:02:11.080 --> 00:02:13.240
was being crushed to dust alive.

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:14.920
Even her right to feel pain

00:02:14.920 --> 00:02:16.840
was laughed at by those animals

00:02:16.840 --> 00:02:18.440
and trampled into the mud.

00:02:24.320 --> 00:02:26.120
If it weren't for those animals,

00:02:26.720 --> 00:02:28.120
we could still be like before,

00:02:28.120 --> 00:02:29.720
rehearsing plays together,

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:31.560
crying together,

00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:33.570
and laughing together.

00:02:34.760 --> 00:02:35.840
But now,

00:02:36.680 --> 00:02:39.079
she has been so easily forgotten.

00:02:42.840 --> 00:02:44.760
Because in their lives,

00:02:45.079 --> 00:02:46.810
she meant absolutely nothing.

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:48.920
Guan Jing died,

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:50.079
and there's me.

00:02:50.920 --> 00:02:52.560
If I die, there are countless other girls

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:54.220
for them to amuse themselves,

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:55.079
play with,

00:02:55.480 --> 00:02:56.680
and brutally murder.

00:03:00.520 --> 00:03:02.720
Then let's use our rotten flesh,

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:05.440
dipped in Guan Jing's blood,

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:09.120
to light a fire that burns through hell.

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:13.560
Let those animals taste

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:16.440
what it's like to be crushed to dust.

00:03:48.040 --> 00:03:48.560
Sun Xun,

00:03:48.800 --> 00:03:50.160
evacuate the crowd immediately.

00:03:50.160 --> 00:03:51.440
Everyone, stay away from me.

00:03:51.440 --> 00:03:52.480
Go catch Zhou Guannan.

00:03:52.480 --> 00:03:53.240
He just ran off,

00:03:53.240 --> 00:03:54.520
no more than five minutes ago.

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:55.650
Call the bomb squad.

00:03:55.800 --> 00:03:56.560
Everyone else,

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:57.240
evacuate.

00:03:58.120 --> 00:03:58.560
Go.

00:03:59.120 --> 00:04:00.080
Suspect Zhou Guannan

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:02.040
left Number 6 Sanhe Street about five minutes ago.

00:04:02.040 --> 00:04:03.120
Pursue along the streets immediately

00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:03.920
and set up checkpoints.

00:04:03.920 --> 00:04:04.600
Also note that

00:04:04.600 --> 00:04:06.040
the suspect is good at disguises.

00:04:06.040 --> 00:04:06.800
All units, pay attention

00:04:06.800 --> 00:04:07.800
and screen carefully.

00:04:07.800 --> 00:04:08.600
Hello, comrade.

00:04:08.600 --> 00:04:10.600
Routine check. Please show your ID.

00:04:12.080 --> 00:04:13.010
Don't come over.

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:13.960
Leave quickly.

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:14.440
Go.

00:04:14.880 --> 00:04:15.440
Shut up.

00:04:16.320 --> 00:04:17.579
It's useless, Sun Xun.

00:04:17.640 --> 00:04:19.170
Don't waste your time on me.

00:04:22.240 --> 00:04:24.240
It's no use. You leave quickly.

00:04:24.280 --> 00:04:25.140
Leave me alone.

00:04:25.160 --> 00:04:26.020
Leave quickly.

00:04:27.400 --> 00:04:28.860
Are you the captain or am I?

00:04:28.920 --> 00:04:29.560
Why should I listen to you?

00:04:29.560 --> 00:04:30.520
Leave quickly.

00:04:33.360 --> 00:04:33.960
Stop arguing.

00:04:33.960 --> 00:04:35.490
I can definitely defuse it.

00:04:35.920 --> 00:04:36.720
Don't forget,

00:04:37.080 --> 00:04:38.600
I took first place in bomb disposal class

00:04:38.600 --> 00:04:39.840
every single year.

00:04:45.240 --> 00:04:45.880
Sun Xun.

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:47.180
Hurry up and leave.

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:48.640
I don't want to get anyone else killed.

00:04:48.640 --> 00:04:49.480
You won't. Trust me.

00:04:49.480 --> 00:04:50.440
I don't want to get anyone...

00:04:50.440 --> 00:04:51.200
No.

00:04:52.440 --> 00:04:53.040
You won't.

00:04:54.080 --> 00:04:55.140
I won't be like you,

00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:58.400
living the rest of my life in regret.

00:04:58.640 --> 00:05:01.500
Regretting that I wasn't the one killed by the bomb.

00:05:02.520 --> 00:05:03.850
We both need to survive.

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:05.960
I've been a cop for so many years.

00:05:05.960 --> 00:05:08.290
I've long forgotten what giving up means.

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:10.060
The case isn't solved yet,

00:05:10.080 --> 00:05:11.640
and the killer hasn't been caught.

00:05:11.640 --> 00:05:12.400
The two of us,

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:14.120
we have to keep going.

00:05:56.200 --> 00:05:57.159
There's no time.

00:05:59.200 --> 00:05:59.880
Sun Xun.

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:01.700
Get out of here.

00:06:02.520 --> 00:06:03.380
Hurry up and go.

00:06:04.520 --> 00:06:05.320
There's no time.

00:06:05.320 --> 00:06:06.360
Go.

00:06:06.880 --> 00:06:07.640
Go.

00:06:07.880 --> 00:06:09.480
Let me just ask you one thing.

00:06:09.960 --> 00:06:10.840
Do you trust me?

00:06:13.480 --> 00:06:13.880
Come on.

00:06:13.880 --> 00:06:14.360
Let's go.

00:06:14.360 --> 00:06:14.840
Hurry up.

00:06:14.840 --> 00:06:16.370
Come on, keep up in the back.

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:17.800
Come on, let's go.

00:06:19.200 --> 00:06:21.330
Why aren't Captain Sun and Yan out yet?

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:23.800
Do you think they can defuse the bomb inside?

00:06:23.800 --> 00:06:24.400
I don't know.

00:06:24.400 --> 00:06:25.760
But Captain Sun specifically ordered

00:06:25.760 --> 00:06:26.680
to have all the civilians

00:06:26.680 --> 00:06:27.440
completely evacuated.

00:06:27.440 --> 00:06:28.680
He was afraid of involving others.

00:06:28.680 --> 00:06:29.240
Let's go check again.

00:06:29.240 --> 00:06:29.680
Go.

00:06:34.680 --> 00:06:35.610
Don't hesitate.

00:06:37.080 --> 00:06:37.640
Cut it.

00:06:52.520 --> 00:06:53.159
Cut it.

00:06:53.960 --> 00:06:55.490
Don't hesitate, cut it now.

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:03.360
Cut it.

00:07:09.240 --> 00:07:09.920
Yan.

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:11.400
Master.

00:07:12.560 --> 00:07:13.760
Let it go completely.

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:16.730
You can't live in the past forever.

00:07:39.320 --> 00:07:40.000
Move.

00:08:18.400 --> 00:08:19.160
Zhou Guannan

00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:22.040
doesn't really want me dead.

00:08:22.960 --> 00:08:23.920
This kid

00:08:24.480 --> 00:08:25.810
still has a conscience.

00:08:28.160 --> 00:08:29.690
He's buying time to escape.

00:08:30.280 --> 00:08:31.680
Where would he escape to?

00:09:33.960 --> 00:09:34.280
Yan,

00:09:34.280 --> 00:09:34.600
Captain Sun.

00:09:34.600 --> 00:09:35.600
What did you find?

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:38.130
We found clothes that might be the suspect's.

00:09:38.640 --> 00:09:40.570
He's already changed his clothes.

00:09:41.160 --> 00:09:42.160
Step up the investigation.

00:09:42.160 --> 00:09:44.420
Conduct a carpet search of the vicinity.

00:09:45.160 --> 00:09:45.890
Captain Sun.

00:09:46.040 --> 00:09:46.800
The traffic police

00:09:46.800 --> 00:09:48.000
tracked through road surveillance

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:50.080
and found Zhou Guannan's last traces.

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:52.280
He headed towards the sunflower field.

00:10:29.320 --> 00:10:30.380
Call an ambulance.

00:10:30.680 --> 00:10:31.740
Call an ambulance.

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:24.860
Did he really commit suicide?

00:11:29.320 --> 00:11:31.080
No footprints of a second person

00:11:31.080 --> 00:11:32.410
were found at the scene.

00:11:32.880 --> 00:11:34.280
Traces can be covered up.

00:11:35.280 --> 00:11:36.760
If he really wanted to die,

00:11:37.800 --> 00:11:39.520
why did he tie a fake bomb

00:11:40.120 --> 00:11:41.440
on me

00:11:42.680 --> 00:11:44.280
to buy time to escape?

00:11:49.120 --> 00:11:50.450
And that pot of flowers.

00:11:51.200 --> 00:11:52.880
When we finally found it,

00:11:54.520 --> 00:11:56.000
where was that pot of flowers?

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:58.520
That pot of flowers must be very important to him.

00:11:58.520 --> 00:12:00.250
He wouldn't just throw it away.

00:12:01.920 --> 00:12:03.050
That pot of flowers,

00:12:04.360 --> 00:12:05.690
what does it represent?

00:12:27.280 --> 00:12:29.210
There's still something missing.

00:12:30.840 --> 00:12:32.040
Behind Zhou Guannan,

00:12:33.680 --> 00:12:35.000
there hides a shadow.

00:13:02.640 --> 00:13:04.440
The surveillance footage shows

00:13:04.560 --> 00:13:05.820
at this intersection,

00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:07.480
he was holding that potted daisy.

00:13:07.480 --> 00:13:08.640
But at the next intersection,

00:13:08.640 --> 00:13:09.760
it was gone.

00:13:10.640 --> 00:13:11.770
Where is the flower?

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:15.560
He must have stopped

00:13:15.680 --> 00:13:16.610
along this road.

00:13:17.320 --> 00:13:18.450
Let's go take a look.

00:13:28.720 --> 00:13:29.780
This pot of flowers

00:13:30.040 --> 00:13:32.170
looks very similar to Zhou Guannan's.

00:13:33.760 --> 00:13:34.680
Officers,

00:13:34.880 --> 00:13:36.340
why don't you come inside?

00:13:36.840 --> 00:13:37.240
Ah.

00:13:38.120 --> 00:13:39.320
What brings you here?

00:13:39.360 --> 00:13:40.080
We were just passing by.

00:13:40.080 --> 00:13:40.920
Since you're back,

00:13:40.920 --> 00:13:42.160
can I ask,

00:13:42.800 --> 00:13:43.520
what kind of flower

00:13:43.520 --> 00:13:44.320
is this?

00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:45.400
Oh.

00:13:45.400 --> 00:13:47.200
It's just an ordinary daisy.

00:13:47.360 --> 00:13:48.520
You can find it in many flower shops.

00:13:48.520 --> 00:13:49.120
Why?

00:13:49.400 --> 00:13:50.120
If you like it,

00:13:50.120 --> 00:13:51.380
I can give you two pots.

00:13:52.480 --> 00:13:53.080
It's nothing.

00:13:53.080 --> 00:13:53.920
They are quite pretty.

00:13:53.920 --> 00:13:54.720
Just got back?

00:13:54.840 --> 00:13:55.520
Oh, right.

00:13:56.040 --> 00:13:58.280
My fiancé took me to pick out wedding rings.

00:13:58.280 --> 00:13:59.960
He only likes Sophia's limited editions.

00:13:59.960 --> 00:14:01.960
He insisted on taking me to see them.

00:14:04.480 --> 00:14:05.320
That Lu Wei,

00:14:05.760 --> 00:14:07.800
he ran over and killed someone a while ago.

00:14:07.800 --> 00:14:09.040
After that person died,

00:14:09.040 --> 00:14:10.770
he gave Shuping a diamond ring.

00:14:10.920 --> 00:14:11.850
It was quite big.

00:14:12.240 --> 00:14:13.680
He's just a truck driver.

00:14:13.960 --> 00:14:15.360
How could he afford that?

00:14:15.440 --> 00:14:17.240
He must have done something bad.

00:14:20.360 --> 00:14:20.890
Ah, okay.

00:14:21.120 --> 00:14:22.040
We won't hold you up.

00:14:22.040 --> 00:14:23.100
We'll be going now.

00:14:30.920 --> 00:14:31.520
Xiaohan,

00:14:31.920 --> 00:14:33.880
the diamond ring found at Pan Shuping's place,

00:14:33.880 --> 00:14:35.000
and the one I sent you yesterday,

00:14:35.000 --> 00:14:36.240
the diamond ring on Qiao Sisi's hand,

00:14:36.240 --> 00:14:37.320
did you look into them?

00:14:37.320 --> 00:14:37.960
I checked.

00:14:38.040 --> 00:14:40.200
They are both limited editions released by Sophia this year.

00:14:40.200 --> 00:14:41.160
Because they are quite expensive,

00:14:41.160 --> 00:14:42.160
very few people bought them.

00:14:42.160 --> 00:14:43.240
However, this diamond ring,

00:14:43.240 --> 00:14:44.560
in the Jiangzhou area this year,

00:14:44.560 --> 00:14:45.840
only one was sold.

00:14:45.840 --> 00:14:47.560
Why do both Pan Shuping and Qiao Sisi have it?

00:14:47.560 --> 00:14:49.360
Jiang-E 59888.

00:14:49.400 --> 00:14:50.600
This is my fiancé.

00:14:50.960 --> 00:14:52.080
He insisted on taking me to see

00:14:52.080 --> 00:14:54.340
Sophia's limited edition wedding ring.

00:14:55.720 --> 00:14:57.980
So the diamond ring Wang Qiang mentioned

00:14:58.040 --> 00:14:59.440
is actually Qiao Sisi's.

00:14:59.560 --> 00:15:00.280
It was Lu Wei

00:15:00.400 --> 00:15:02.800
who pulled it off Qiao Sisi's severed hand.

00:15:02.960 --> 00:15:03.840
To be exact,

00:15:03.960 --> 00:15:06.520
the diamond ring was given to Li Ting by Wang Zhiwei.

00:15:06.520 --> 00:15:08.520
While searching Zhou Guannan's house last night,

00:15:08.520 --> 00:15:10.040
I saw in his murder video

00:15:10.240 --> 00:15:12.160
that Qiao Sisi was wearing

00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:13.320
a diamond ring.

00:15:14.080 --> 00:15:16.740
But we didn't find that diamond ring at the time.

00:15:17.960 --> 00:15:20.000
Now, combined with Wang Qiang's testimony, we can be sure.

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:21.200
Lu Wei is not a coward.

00:15:21.360 --> 00:15:22.960
After accidentally running over the body,

00:15:22.960 --> 00:15:24.400
he took advantage of the situation,

00:15:24.400 --> 00:15:25.660
took the diamond ring,

00:15:25.800 --> 00:15:27.260
and gave it to Pan Shuping.

00:15:27.800 --> 00:15:29.400
The diamond ring is a limited edition,

00:15:29.400 --> 00:15:30.960
and it was a gift from her fiancé.

00:15:30.960 --> 00:15:33.560
So Li Ting wouldn't give it to Qiao Sisi easily.

00:15:33.920 --> 00:15:34.850
Do you remember?

00:15:35.360 --> 00:15:36.560
We once found out that

00:15:37.720 --> 00:15:38.640
before the incident,

00:15:38.640 --> 00:15:40.770
every month, Qiao Sisi's bank account

00:15:40.800 --> 00:15:42.240
would receive an overseas

00:15:42.240 --> 00:15:42.970
remittance.

00:15:43.040 --> 00:15:43.640
Overseas.

00:15:44.040 --> 00:15:46.120
Given Qiao Sisi's social circle, how could she have overseas contacts?

00:15:46.120 --> 00:15:46.800
Did you check it?

00:15:46.800 --> 00:15:48.800
We have sent a request to our partner units for a joint investigation.

00:15:48.800 --> 00:15:49.760
But since it involves overseas elements,

00:15:49.760 --> 00:15:50.760
it's quite complicated.

00:15:50.760 --> 00:15:53.220
So we might not get results in the short term.

00:15:53.440 --> 00:15:55.760
This morning I received the joint investigation results from our sister department.

00:15:55.760 --> 00:15:57.680
It shows that the overseas account

00:15:57.680 --> 00:15:58.880
was opened by Wang Zhiwei

00:15:58.880 --> 00:15:59.960
for Li Ting.

00:16:00.080 --> 00:16:00.720
So,

00:16:01.080 --> 00:16:02.480
it was actually Qiao Sisi

00:16:02.600 --> 00:16:03.960
who was blackmailing Li Ting.

00:16:03.960 --> 00:16:05.360
Whether it's blackmail or not,

00:16:05.360 --> 00:16:06.420
Li Ting is probably

00:16:06.600 --> 00:16:07.520
the key to

00:16:07.520 --> 00:16:08.400
this case.